{"tid":260103,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"宇宙大爆炸理論","createTime":"2017-05-27T12:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T13:02:58.000Z","uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"422bff42b44149f2a6786453206e947fa18dda0a","tid":260103,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"其實大爆炸理論最多只能夠解釋到物質和能量為什麼出現，但不能夠解釋一切定律和數學關系從何而來，如果沒有這些宇宙定律，大爆炸是沒有用的。物質加上能量，還需要充滿智慧的定律和數學規律才會形成現在的宇宙形態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yO9BwNWDfm4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyO9BwNWDfm4&d=dOZkJEEeTMgEOzb72xmK%2FDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c7e08bfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yO9BwNWDfm4</a><br />\n<br />\n數學奇妙規律<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U9YQrAB2HWk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DU9YQrAB2HWk&d=dOZkJEEeTMgEOzb72xmK%2FDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8f97d3a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U9YQrAB2HWk</a><br />\n<br />\n唔通爆炸可以炸出經典力學、狹義相對論、量子力學、熱力學、聲學、光學、電磁學入面充滿智慧既規律?<br />\n<br />\n萬有引力呢一個設定係可以爆出黎?"},{"pid":"44765998d8cdc1be742713e3aa6715b549dd7149","tid":260103,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"grand unified theory"},{"pid":"f4ef6462e9c025e2b5cad145fcfe6e0a5b9c7867","tid":260103,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>grand unified theory</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大一統理論當中嘅規律可以經由爆炸產生？"},{"pid":"6ff51cc9439a3159c0f238353abea6617fcef952","tid":260103,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"二次大戰響日本爆果兩個原子彈爆左乜野新物理定律出黎？"}]}